details.purpose: For recording an accident or exposure leading to one or more injuries.

items.items: An injury or illness which is deemed by a clinician to have arisen at least in part from an accident or exposure
The accident, injurious event(s) or exposure that occurred
The date of that the injury occurred or began
The age at the time of injury or onset of injurous events
Description of the accident or exposure
Details of any factors contributing to the illness or injury
The factor that contributed to the cause of the injury
Details of health problems or diagnoses arising from the injury
The problem or a link to the problem described elsewhere in the EHR
The contribution of this factor to the severity of the injury or illness
Major contribution to the severity of the illness
Minor contribution to the severity of injury or illness
The category of effect of the injury on the course or progression
Permanent alteration of the course or progression of the medical condition
Temporary alteration of the course or progression of the medical condition
The description of the effect on the existing problem
The insurance type that is relevent ot this injury
Insurance covering injuries and exposures at work
Individual insurance to cover injury and exposure
Insurance to cover for permanent disability
Insurance covering accident and injury while travelling
Department of Veterans Affairs accepted disability (White card)
Information about the type of cover or restrictions
The date of acceptance/approval of the insurance claim by the insurance company
The date that the claim is finally closed
Details of the employer associated with the claim
Details of the person managing this claim for the employer
The person in the workplace who directly supervises the injured worker
Information about employer(s) not involved in insurance claim
Employer not involved in insurance claim
Description of the occuption at the time of injury
The date of onset of the injury or illness arising
The date of onset of the effect on an existing problem
The place where the accident or exposure occurred
